Title: Age Before Beauty
Plot: When young super models rapidly age 50 years overnight, Pete and Myka go undercover in the glam world of high fashion to discover who ? and what ? is behind the transformations.
GuestStars: Tawny Cypress, Phillip Rhys, Nolan Gerard Funk, Salvatore Antonio, Natalie Krill, Robin Kasyanov, Erica Cox, Shauna MacDonald
